    "93378651": {
      "title": "Drying: principles, applications and design",
      "abstract": "This textbook is a compilation of information on drying theory and practice. The contents include drying kinetics, material and gas properties, heat and mass transfer in drying processes and dispersion dryers, and highlights the principles of efficient and economic dryer design. This text is designed to be an introduction and guide on drying principles and applications."
